10 I sáid: In the mídst of my dáys I must depárt.
I am consígned to the gátes of Shéol
for the rést of my yéars.

11 I sáid, I shall not sée
the Lórd in the lánd of the líving;
nó móre shall I lóok on the húman ráce,
on thóse who inhábit the wórld.

12 My dwélling is pulled úp and remóved from mé
Í like a shépherd's tént;
! hé has rolled úp my lífe like a wéaver,
who sévers me from the lást thréad.

16 O Lórd, in yóu my héart hópes,
my spírit líves;
héal me and gíve me lífe.
